<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Hugo - 标签 - Luhong's Blog</title><link>https://1104381746.github.io/hugo-blog/tags/hugo/</link><description>Hugo - 标签 - Luhong's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://1104381746.github.io/hugo-blog/tags/hugo/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>博客搭建完成 🎉</title><link>https://1104381746.github.io/hugo-blog/hello/</link><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Luhong</author><guid>https://1104381746.github.io/hugo-blog/hello/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h2 id="博客架构">博客架构</h2>
<p>本博客基于以下技术栈搭建：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Obsidian</strong> — 笔记编辑与管理</li>
<li><strong>GitHub Sync</strong> — 全量备份到 GitHub</li>
<li><strong>Enveloppe</strong> — 选择性发布笔记到博客</li>
<li><strong>Hugo</strong> + <strong>LoveIt 主题</strong> — 静态站点生成</li>
<li><strong>GitHub Pages</strong> — 自动部署与托管</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="发布流程">发布流程</h2>
<ol>
<li>在 Obsidian 中写好笔记</li>
<li>frontmatter 添加 <code>share: true</code></li>
<li>右键 → Enveloppe → Share this file</li>
<li>GitHub Actions 自动构建部署</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="后续计划">后续计划</h2>
<ul>
<li>配置评论系统（giscus）</li>
<li>自定义域名</li>
<li>持续优化主题样式</li>
</ul>]]></description></item></channel></rss>